CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: PACS Group, Inc. is a holding company investing in post-acute healthcare facilities, professionals, and ancillary services. Founded in 2013, PACS Group is one of the largest post-acute platforms in the United States. Its independent subsidiaries operate post-acute care facilities across nine states serving over 20,000 patients daily.
